space       toggle selection of current entry
v           inverts selections in current directory
u           unmark all selections

y           copy current entry or selections
d           cut current entry or selections
p           paste copied or cut entries to current directory
c           clear selections

ctrl + u    move half page up
ctrl + b    move half page down
ctrl + b    move full page up
ctrl + f    move full page down

gg          move to top
G           move to bottom

$           `shell` runs command in shell
%           `shell-pipe` runs command in shell while piping in and out
!           `shell-wait` runs command in shell and waits for key press afterwards
&           `shell-async` runs command in background

sn          sort by name
ss          sort by size
st          sort by time
